HEADWORD: Choking
<hw>Chok"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>That
chokes; producing the feeling of strangulation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Indistinct in utterance, as the voice of a person
affected with strong emotion.</def></p>

